headline.main: AXIS SEES 'BLUFF' IN ALLIED WARNING; Berlin Predicts War of Nerves Will Follow the Parley -- 'Fantastic,' Says Tokyo

lead_paragraph: LONDON, Dec. 2 (AP) -- German propagandists galloped in all directions today seeking to counteract the effect of the North African conference, describing it both as an empty bluff and as a prelude to a war of nerves.
abstract: Ger comment on Cairo conf and alleged Teheran conf
